<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <title>Smells Like Bakin</title>

  <link rel="stylesheet" href="<%= stylesheet_path 'application' %>">
  <script src="<%= javascript_path 'application' %>"></script>
</head>

<body>
  <div class="container clearfix">
    <div class="main-logo grid_4">
      <object class="img-container"
              data="<%= image_path "logos/logo.svg" %>"
              type="image/svg+xml" class="logo">
      </object>
    </div>

    <div class="nav grid_8 omega">
      <ul>
        <li class="about"><a href="/">About</a></li>
        <li class="pricing"><a href="/pricing">Cupcakes & Prices</a></li>
        <li class="locations"><a href="/locations">Locations</a></li>
        <li class="contact"><a href="/contact">Contact Us</a></li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <%= yield %>

    <div id="about" class="grid_7">
      <h2 class="giga">Inside the Kitchen</h2>
      <p>
      Smells Like Bakin’ started out in the garage of the husband wife duo
      Allison &amp; Joseph. Allison is the baker, and Joseph found a way for
      them to make a business out of her tasty treats. Flash forward to 
      today and they have a successful store front, catering business and 
      cupcake truck.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="grid_5 omega">
      <h2 class="giga">Get Bakin’ with Us</h2>

      <div>
        <p>
          Call us: <span class="phone">1-800-CUP-CAKE</span><br>
          Email us: <a class="avocato" href="#">bakeon@smellslikebakin.com</a>
        </p>
      </div>

      <p>
        We announce all of our new flavors first through Facebook &amp; 
        Twitter, and even take requests!
      </p>

      <object class="img-container"
              data="<%= image_path 'logos/facebook.svg' %>"
              type="image/svg+xml">
      </object>

      <object class="img-container"
              data="<%= image_path 'logos/twitter.svg' %>"
              type="image/svg+xml">
      </object>
    </div>

    <div class="copyright grid_12">
      <p>© 2012 Smells Like Bakin' Cupcake Company. All Rights Reserved.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
